Package: thumbsup-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.8), avahi-utils, nfs-common
Description: Secure NAS client for ThumbsUp devices
 ThumbsUp Client provides secure, certificate-based access to ThumbsUp
 NAS devices on your local network. It uses mDNS for automatic device
 discovery and mTLS for authentication.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic server discovery via mDNS/Avahi
  - Mutual TLS (mTLS) certificate-based authentication
  - NFS file sharing with automatic mounting
  - Support for multiple ThumbsUp devices
